jemmet is the HTTP edge of a three-project Lean stack and consumes, as vendored
pinned dependencies (added at later milestones), the sibling projects:
  - iotakt  — non-blocking I/O   (Apache-2.0)
  - kroopt  — TLS secure channel (Apache-2.0)
Their licenses and notices accompany their vendored sources when introduced.
